OL,3,CSchools dropping subjects because of
OL,4,Cteacher recruitment and retention `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FTeachers are taking classes outside
OL,8,Ftheir specialism and some schools are
OL,9,Fdropping subjects entirely because of
OL,10,Fteacher recruitment and retention
OL,11,Fissues, a report has found.
OL,13,FThe Education Committee has called on
OL,14,Fthe Government to invest in programmes
OL,15,Fto boost recruitment, training and
OL,16,Fretention in the teaching profession
OL,17,Fin a report published on Friday.
