OL,3,CSchools dropping subjects because of
OL,4,Cteacher recruitment and retention `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FRecruitment targets for initial
OL,8,Fteacher training courses were missed
OL,9,Fin 10 subjects in 2022/23, according
OL,10,Fto the committee, with maths, physics
OL,11,Fand religious education among the
OL,12,Fsubjects affected.
OL,14,F"While there have been welcome
OL,15,Fincreases in absolute teacher numbers,
OL,16,Fthese have not kept pace with pupil
OL,17,Fnumbers, and there is broad agreement
OL,18,Ffrom witnesses that there is a crisis
OL,19,Fof teacher recruitment and retention
OL,20,Fin England," the report said.
