OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FIt added: "We have significant
OL,8,Fconcerns about the negative impacts of
OL,9,Fsubject specific teacher shortages.
OL,11,F"These include compromising the
OL,12,Fquality of teaching where subjects are
OL,13,Fbeing taught by teachers without
OL,14,Fsubject expertise and the reduction of
OL,15,Fsubject provision where schools do not
OL,16,Fhave sufficient specialist teaching
OL,17,Fcapacity.
OL,19,F"We also heard that lack of specialist
OL,20,Fteachers can have an adverse impact on
OL,21,Ftake-up of certain subjects."
