OL,7,FThe committee recommended bursaries
OL,8,Fdeveloped by the Government to address
OL,9,Fsubject specific teacher shortages be
OL,10,Fexpanded and increased, and that
OL,11,Fprogrammes allowing for alternative
OL,12,Froutes into the profession are
OL,13,Freinstated.
OL,15,FEducation Committee chairman Robin
OL,16,FWalker said: "Ministers need to
OL,17,Frethink the recent, short-sighted cuts
OL,18,Fto programmes that promoted career
OL,19,Fdevelopment and different routes into
OL,20,Fthe profession.
