OL,7,F"Without them we will keep on missing
OL,8,Ftargets for recruiting specialist
OL,9,Fteachers in nearly every subject,
OL,10,Fforcing more teachers to take on
OL,11,Fclasses outside of their specialism
OL,12,Fand thereby undermining the quality of
OL,13,Feducation children receive."
OL,15,FAccording to the committee, many
OL,16,Fcurrent teachers singled out
OL,17,F"excessive workloads" rather than pay
OL,18,Fas the biggest factor pushing them to
OL,19,Fleave the sector.
