OL,7,FIn the Department for Education's
OL,8,F(DfE) 2022 Working Lives of Teachers
OL,9,Fsurvey, 92% of participating teachers
OL,10,Fcited workload as a reason to quit the
OL,11,Fprofession, while 57% cited pay.
OL,13,FCharity Education Support told the
OL,14,Fcommittee that additional workload can
OL,15,Fbe "associated with accountability
OL,16,Fmeasures, particularly Ofsted
OL,17,Finspections".
