OL,7,FThe report recommended the department
OL,8,Fincrease "myth-busting efforts" around
OL,9,FOfsted to "reduce accountability
OL,10,Frelated workload".
OL,12,FTeachers were found to be dedicating
OL,13,Fmore time to offering students mental
OL,14,Fhealth support and family conflict
OL,15,Fresolution since the pandemic, with
OL,16,FEducation Support also saying teachers
OL,17,Fwere helping children to combat the
OL,18,Fcost-of-living crisis by buying meals
OL,19,Fand washing uniforms.
OL,26,@pD@JOUpD@_O]qD@KOUrD@QO]
