OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe committee recommended the DfE
OL,8,Fdefines the remit of schools' and
OL,9,Fteachers' responsibilities and ensures
OL,10,F"wraparound support" delivered by
OL,11,Fappropriate organisations is made more
OL,12,Fwidely available.
OL,14,FPupil behaviour has also worsened
OL,15,Fsince the pandemic, according to the
OL,16,Freport, which can "discourage" people
OL,17,Ffrom becoming teachers and make
OL,18,Fexisting teachers think about leaving
OL,19,Fthe profession.
