OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FIt was recommended that the Government
OL,8,Fexpand its Behaviour Hubs programme,
OL,9,Fwhich helps school leaders to create
OL,10,Fpositive school environments, to allow
OL,11,Fmore schools to benefit from it.
OL,13,FThe report also said teacher salaries
OL,14,F"need to be attractive" to boost
OL,15,Frecruitment and that while the
OL,16,Fintroduction of a #30,000 starting
OL,17,Fsalary was a welcome step, the figure
OL,18,Fwill have to increase in the coming
OL,19,Fyears "if it is to remain competitive".
