OL,7,FThe Association of School and College
OL,8,FLeaders said the Education Committee
OL,9,Fidentified the problem "but not the
OL,10,Fsolution".
OL,12,FGeneral secretary Pepe Di'Iasio said:
OL,13,F"Piecemeal incentives to get and keep
OL,14,Fpeople in teaching are not working,
OL,15,Fand excessive workload can only be
OL,16,Ffully addressed by schools having
OL,17,Fenough money to afford enough staff,
OL,18,Fwhich is currently not the case.
OL,26,@qD@XOUrD@IO]uD@AOU
