OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"This comes down to funding, for pay
OL,8,Fwhich is sufficient to attract and
OL,9,Fretain teachers, and to properly
OL,10,Fresource schools. But the financial
OL,11,Fposition is actually getting worse,
OL,12,Fnot better, with many schools setting
OL,13,Fdeficit budgets while they make more
OL,14,Fcuts.
OL,16,F"You cannot turn around an ocean liner
OL,17,Fwithout enough fuel, and the current
OL,18,Fgovernment just does not understand
OL,19,Fthat."
