OL,7,FPaul Whiteman, general secretary at
OL,8,Fschool leaders' union NAHT, said:
OL,9,F"Above all the Government needs to act
OL,10,Fdecisively to address the 'big ticket'
OL,11,Fissues which are making it harder than
OL,12,Fever for schools to attract and keep
OL,13,Fthe teachers they need, including not
OL,14,Fonly workload, but the damage
OL,15,Finflicted by the brutal Ofsted
OL,16,Finspection regime and years of real-
OL,17,Fterms pay cuts."
