OL,7,F"Last autumn the Government delivered
OL,8,Fon its commitment, giving all new
OL,9,Fteachers a starting salary of at least
OL,10,F#30,000. We are also taking steps to
OL,11,Fsupport teachers' wellbeing and ease
OL,12,Fworkload pressures, including plans to
OL,13,Fsupport schools to reduce working
OL,14,Fhours by five hours per week."
